// Test even number check with inline expression

store num as 1
display "Testing 1:"
check if ((num divided by 2) times 2) is equal to num:
    display "  -> 1 is EVEN (WRONG!)"
otherwise:
    display "  -> 1 is ODD (correct)"
end check

change num to 2
display "Testing 2:"
check if ((num divided by 2) times 2) is equal to num:
    display "  -> 2 is EVEN (correct)"
otherwise:
    display "  -> 2 is ODD (WRONG!)"
end check

change num to 3
display "Testing 3:"
check if ((num divided by 2) times 2) is equal to num:
    display "  -> 3 is EVEN (WRONG!)"
otherwise:
    display "  -> 3 is ODD (correct)"
end check
